name: Korean Air A330-223 [HL8211] Windy Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Every summer since 2015, Korean Air has operated 3 charter flights to Calgary from Seoul-Incheon with their Airbus A330-200. Even though Calgary now has a second connection to Asia through Hainan, it's always nice to see Korean Air here, even just on an annual basis. Here is our third and final flight of the year from Korean, operated by HL8211 from Seoul-Incheon this afternoon in some windy conditions! ATC is included,  hope you all enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
